  <bioghist id="aspace_82a2f9439bc379d081696f5c06e6e434">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Richard M. Juang and W. Carter Smith originated the idea for this conference and were part of the Organizing Committee.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_934b887e5bc7cd023719f8d7c8af1988">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Richard M. Juang's planning documents for the TransPositions conference that took place at Cornell University on March 27-29, 1998. Also, the program and the curriculum vitae and speeches of some of the speakers.</p>  </scopecontent>
